# tmpl

**tmpl** - Generates [mkstemp(3)](https://man.openbsd.org/mkstemp) file and writes output of `PROGRAM` to it

## Build

### compile
```
# ./bootstrap
# ./configure ...
# make
```

### install
```
# sudo make install
```
